---
// Componente de experiencia profesional
---

<section id="experience" class="section py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary to-black/80">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="text-primary">Experiencia</span> Profesional
      </h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-300 max-w-3xl">
        Un recorrido por mi experiencia laboral y los roles que he desempeñado como desarrollador y administrador de sistemas.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Línea vertical del timeline -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/80 to-primary/30"></div>
      
      <!-- Timeline items -->
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right mb-8 md:mb-0">
            <div class="card hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">AgriNews</h3>
              <h4 class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Desarrollador FullStack (Actual)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Desarrollo de aplicaciones web utilizando tecnologías modernas y colaboración en proyectos de transformación digital del sector agrícola.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4 md:justify-end">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">.NET</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">IA</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Backend</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400 md:hidden mb-4">2023 - Actual</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400 hidden md:block">2023 - Actual</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right order-1 md:order-1 mb-8 md:mb-0 hidden md:block">
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400">2021 - 2023</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center z-10 order-2 md:order-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 order-3 md:order-3">
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400 md:hidden mb-4">2021 - 2023</div>
            <div class="card hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Administrador de Sistemas</h3>
              <h4 class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Empresa IT</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Gestión de infraestructura IT, resolución de incidencias y mantenimiento de sistemas. Implementación de mejoras en los procesos tecnológicos.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Sistemas</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Redes</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">IT</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right mb-8 md:mb-0">
            <div class="card hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Empresariales</h3>
              <h4 class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Proyecto Regional</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Desarrollo de aplicaciones empresariales líderes en la región Balcánica, mejora de sistemas existentes y colaboración en proyectos.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4 md:justify-end">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">React</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Laravel</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Web</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400 md:hidden mb-4">2020 - 2021</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400 hidden md:block">2020 - 2021</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Item 4 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right order-1 md:order-1 mb-8 md:mb-0 hidden md:block">
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400">2019 - 2020</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center z-10 order-2 md:order-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 order-3 md:order-3">
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-400 md:hidden mb-4">2019 - 2020</div>
            <div class="card hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Prácticas Formativas</h3>
              <h4 class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Varias empresas</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Prácticas en dos empresas diferentes donde desarrollé habilidades técnicas en mantenimiento de equipos, configuración de redes y atención a usuarios.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Soporte</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Redes</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 border border-blue-800/50">Hardware</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 